<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog it Out</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://pro.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.10.0/css/all.css"
        integrity="sha384-AYmEC3Yw5cVb3ZcuHtOA93w35dYTsvhLPVnYs9eStHfGJvOvKxVfELGroGkvsg+p" crossorigin="anonymous" />

</head>
<style>
    @media(max-width: 998px) {
        html {
            font-size: 65%;
        }
    }
    @media(max-width: 768px)
    {
    html{
        font-size: 45%;
    }
}
    @media(max-width: 450px)
    {
    html{
        font-size: 25%;
    }
}
    .top {
        background-color: rgb(255, 255, 206);
    }

    footer {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100vw;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        padding-top: 40px;
        text-align: center;
        border-bottom: 0.4em solid black;
        background-color: rgba(15, 194, 15, 0.733);
    }

    img {
        height: 10rem;
        width: 10rem;
        margin: 2rem;
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .mid {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 4rem;
    }

    .left {
        position: absolute;
    }

    #insidetop {
        color: red;
        text-align: center;
        margin: auto;
    }

    button {
        display: block;
        width: 30rem;
        border-radius: 4rem;
        margin: 1rem auto;
        background-color: black;
        color: white;
        font-size: 3rem;
    }
    button:hover {
        background-color: rgb(13, 66, 240);
        color: black;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    h1 span{
        color: blue;
    }
    h1{
        display: inline;
        font-size: 5rem;
        background-color: #fff;
        margin: 0.8rem;
        padding: 1rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        width: 60rem;
        align-items: center;
    }
    .top p{
        text-align: center;
        width: 50rem;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 0.8rem;
        width: 50rem;
    }

</style>

<body>
    <div class="top">
        <header>
            <div class="left"><img src="/images/logo.jpeg" alt=""></div>
            <div class="mid">
                <h1>Welcome to <span>Blog it Out. </span></h1>
                <h2>Create your blog here. </h2>
                <p>Welcome! everybody to the blogging website Blog it Out. In this platform you can create blogs, post them and show
                  your blog to the world. So start blogging on any topic you are interested in. </p>
            </div>
        </header>
        <div class="btn">
          <form action="/login" method="get">
                <button type="submit" name="button">Log-in</button>
            </form>
            <form action="/register" method="get">
                <button type="submit" name="button">Register</button>
            </form>

        </div>
        <p id="insidetop">*Already registered users can Login directly.</p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer">
            <h4>Developed by Shourya, Shyantan and Harsh</h4>
            <p>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/" target="_blank" style="color:#e6004c; text-decoration: none;"><i
                        class="fab fa-instagram"></i> Instagram&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/" target="_blank" style="color:#4d4dff; text-decoration: none;"><i
                        class="fab fa-facebook"></i> facebook</a>
                <br>
                Copyright Â© Blog It Out 2021
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>
